if statement
------------
Create a class of if statement

Example
-------
public class ifstatement {
public static void main (String[] args){

System.out.println("The list of statement");
int t = 3;

if(t = 3)
{
System.out.println("The Value is 3");
}
System.out.println("Closing the statement");

Change the value 3 to 10 then the  statement inside the if is skipped.
